name: AlmostMirrors-001
description:
Almost Mirrors is a collection of NFTs with watercolors by Tropical Artist Maxugá Miller. This collection intends to point out which human characteristics primates carry and, based on that, to bring a synthesis of what human subjectivity can be.

This collection was created on Adobe Ps with Mixed Technique Watercolor Emulation. Contains 20 items and is intended for collectors who helped and help build the artist's career.

1600x1600 / 300dpi
